OL,3,CReservoir 'size of Gatwick Airport'
OL,4,Cone step closer to being built
OL,6,FThe building of one of the country's
OL,7,Flargest reservoirs is now one step
OL,8,Fcloser after a judicial review was
OL,9,Fdismissed by the High Court.
OL,11,FThe controversial Thames Water
OL,12,Freservoir near Abingdon is estimated
OL,13,Fto be the size of Gatwick Airport,
OL,14,Fwith walls as high as several double-
OL,15,Fdecker buses.
OL,17,FThe water firm said it will help with
OL,18,Fincreasing demand and climate change
OL,19,Fbut some locals are concerned about
OL,20,Fthe safety of the design and the loss
OL,21,Fof a large area of countryside.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
