OL,3,CReservoir 'size of Gatwick Airport'
OL,4,Cone step closer to being built
OL,6,FThere are also fears of flooding for
OL,7,Fpeople living nearby, due to the
OL,8,Famount of water it would contain.
OL,10,FCampaigners took their case to the
OL,11,Fhigh court, challenging the
OL,12,Fgovernment's decision to approve the
OL,13,Fplans, but that was dismissed and the
OL,14,Fplans can now move on.
OL,16,FIt comes as Thames Water faces more
OL,17,Fthan 17-billion pounds of debt and is
OL,18,Fat risk of nationalisation. There is
OL,19,Falso a hosepipe ban in place for
OL,20,Fcustomers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
