OL,3,CReservoir 'size of Gatwick Airport'
OL,4,Cone step closer to being built
OL,6,FThames Water still needs to submit a
OL,7,Fplanning and maintenance application
OL,8,Fand if it all goes through,
OL,9,Fconstruction could start in 2029.
OL,11,FOlly Glover, Lib Dem MP for Didcot and
OL,12,FWantage, also opposes the plans and
OL,13,Fsaid: "Thames Water's finances are
OL,14,Fvery wobbly and this is going to be a
OL,15,Fproject that is going to cost more
OL,16,Fthan two billion pounds.
OL,18,F"Large infrastructure projects like
OL,19,Fthat in this country don't have a
OL,20,Fgreat record of staying within that
OL,21,Fbudget.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
