OL,3,CReservoir 'size of Gatwick Airport'
OL,4,Cone step closer to being built
OL,6,F"So the point I put to the water and
OL,7,Fflooding minister when I met her on
OL,8,FTuesday is that if Thames Water does
OL,9,Fend up going into special
OL,10,Fadministration, then the government
OL,11,Fcould potentially pick up the cost for
OL,12,Fthat.
OL,14,F"Also people are frustrated with
OL,15,FThames Water sewage dumping, inability
OL,16,Fto deal with water leaks and bills
OL,17,Fgoing up so they don't really look to
OL,18,FThames Water as the company capable of
OL,19,Fdelivering the second-biggest
OL,20,Freservoir in the country which is what
OL,21,Fthis would be."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
