OL,6,FNevil Muncaster, Strategic Water
OL,7,FResources Director for Thames Water
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is a critical project for
OL,9,Fwater supply to make sure people
OL,10,Falways have water to drink and it's
OL,11,Fsafe and secure under all conditions.
OL,13,F"The weather is changing, the
OL,14,Fpopulation is growing, we need to make
OL,15,Fsure we have sufficient water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
