OL,3,CReservoir 'size of Gatwick Airport'
OL,4,Cone step closer to being built
OL,6,F"We've worked hard to halve leakage,
OL,7,Fwe are reducing customer demand but we
OL,8,Fstill need new resources and this is
OL,9,Fwhere the reservoir comes in and
OL,10,Fremember it's a reservoir for the
OL,11,Fsouth east supplying water for 15
OL,12,Fmillion people in the region."
OL,14,FIn a statement, the government said:
OL,15,F"Pressure on our water system is
OL,16,Fskyrocketing because of population
OL,17,Fgrowth and climate change.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
