OL,3,CReservoir 'size of Gatwick Airport'
OL,4,Cone step closer to being built
OL,6,F"That's why 104 billion pounds is
OL,7,Fbeing invested to improve water
OL,8,Finfrastructure, including nine new
OL,9,Freservoirs to secure future supplies
OL,10,Fand to cut leaks.
OL,12,F"We are pleased by the court ruling.
OL,13,FThe proposed project would be subject
OL,14,Fto a consultation and would be
OL,15,Frigorously examined by the Planning
OL,16,FInspectorate before development
OL,17,Fconsent could be granted."
